# DESIGN SYSTEM - Minimal Studio

ALWAYS use this exact styling:

## COLORS:
- Background: bg-black text-white only
- Glass effects: bg-white bg-opacity-10 backdrop-blur-md
- Borders: border border-white border-opacity-20
- Text: white primary, text-neutral-300 secondary

## TYPOGRAPHY:
- Font: Inter only (font-sans)
- Headings: font-medium tracking-tighter leading-tight
- Body text: font-light ou font-normal
- Sizes: text-xs, text-sm, text-lg, text-xl, text-4xl md:text-6xl

## BUTTONS:
- Primary: px-8 py-3 bg-white text-black font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-gray-200 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg
- Secondary: px-8 py-3 bg-white bg-opacity-10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-opacity-20 border border-white border-opacity-20

## INPUTS:
- Base: px-4 py-2 bg-white bg-opacity-10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white border-opacity-20 rounded-lg text-white text-xs placeholder-neutral-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:ring-opacity-30
- Font size: text-xs (small), text-sm (medium)

## SPACING:
- Sections: pt-32 pb-32 md:pt-40 md:pb-40
- Containers: max-w-4xl centered
- Gaps: gap-4, space-x-6
- Margins: mt-6, mt-12, mt-20

## EFFECTS:
- Cards: bg-white bg-opacity-5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg border border-white border-opacity-10
- Shadows: shadow-xl, shadow-2xl
- Blur orbs: w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-white opacity-5 blur-[100px] rounded-full

NEVER use other colors, fonts, or styles. Stick to this system exactly.